  37,95,Qala ataAAbudoona ma tanhitoona
  37,96,WaAllahu khalaqakum wama taAAmaloona
  37,97,Qaloo ibnoo lahu bunyanan faalqoohu fee aljaheemi
  37,98,Faaradoo bihi kaydan fajaAAalnahumu alasfaleena
